Mengenal Api

================

API (Application Programming Interface) adalah set instruksi dan protokol yang memungkinkan berbagai perangkat lunak berkomunikasi dan berinteraksi satu sama lain.

================================

contoh sederhana penggunaan API :

1. link web api nya : https://api.coindesk.com/v1/bpi/currentprice.json
2. buat index.html

index.html :

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Bitcoin Price</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 20px;
        }
        h1 {
            text-align: center;
        }
        .currency {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        .currency label {
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <h1>Bitcoin Price</h1>

    <div class="currency">
        <label>USD:</label>
        <span id="usdRate"></span>
    </div>

    <div class="currency">
        <label>GBP:</label>
        <span id="gbpRate"></span>
    </div>

    <div class="currency">
        <label>EUR:</label>
        <span id="eurRate"></span>
    </div>

    <script>
        // Mengambil data harga Bitcoin dari API CoinDesk
        fetch('https://api.coindesk.com/v1/bpi/currentprice.json')
            .then(response => response.json())
            .then(data => {
                // Mendapatkan data harga Bitcoin dalam berbagai mata uang
                const usdRate = data.bpi.USD.rate;
                const gbpRate = data.bpi.GBP.rate;
                const eurRate = data.bpi.EUR.rate;

                // Menampilkan data harga Bitcoin
                document.getElementById("usdRate").innerText = usdRate;
                document.getElementById("gbpRate").innerText = gbpRate;
                document.getElementById("eurRate").innerText = eurRate;
            })
            .catch(error => {
                console.log('Terjadi kesalahan:', error);
            });
    </script>
</body>
</html>


=========================================================
